      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 April 2003 vol 403 cc10-2WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_10ws' title='Col. 10WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 April 2003 vol 403 c10WS' name='column_10ws' href='#column_10ws' rel='bookmark'>10WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
